{"tid":458544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅范椒芬：全世界都想在中國發展分一杯羹","createTime":"2017-11-05T03:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T03:43:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a17c0881f4144ab27465a6d65b00bad1992e2d70","tid":458544,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171105/s00001/64ebd54f0f05096f9a044dc2931e3b76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171105%2Fs00001%2F64ebd54f0f05096f9a044dc2931e3b76.jpg&h=4af30c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國全國人大常委會昨日正式表決，將內地《國歌法》列入港澳《基本法》附件三。行政會議成員羅范椒芬，認為港人無需要將簡單問題複雜化，指對任何一個國民尊重國家國歌是「全球都有」、「人人都要有的基本行為」。她相信政府不會因播放國歌時不站立便拘捕市民，亦坦言法例不可能包含不同場景，市民應就每一個場合「執生」作合適行為。<br />\n<br />\n被問及如何看待港人擔心「一地兩檢」的問題，羅太表示「自己行得正企得正就不必擔心」，指高鐵帶來很大的方便，亦節省了很多的時間，呼籲港人應看大局。<br />\n<br />\n身兼香港科技園公司主席的羅范椒芬又表示，科技界是無國界，意識形態爭議不是那麽嚴重，現時社會問題愈來愈複雜，需要跨界別研究。<br />\n<br />\n她強調目前「全世界都想在中國發展分一杯羹」，希望港人能以包容心態做事，並表示香港市場小，如果能有效利用國家大市場，將對香港十分有利。"},{"pid":"289e74ba2a035e0ece5c1d3ad9a3f39f63c72785","tid":458544,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171105/s00001/1509850345875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171105%2Fs00001%2F1509850345875&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a9a5a53a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171105%2Fs00001%2F1509850345875&h=fbc661de\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171105/s00001/1509850345875</a>"},{"pid":"faff10065a4135f7c0769dbf5820e7045e707643","tid":458544,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"想分左隻雞黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87de44b02d3c4849be9eba5725a6905021429463","tid":458544,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"正確係全世界都想在中國重新劃分勢力範圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}